law.history: Repealed 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 106, sec. 13, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 149, sec. 8, effective June 17, 1954.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Cabinet to certify valuation of watercraft to county clerks -- Filing of certification.
metadata.lrc-note: (6/20/2005). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 106 prevails over its amendment in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85.
